*event_1
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

[texton]
[b]Lost Forest ahead, do not enter![/b]
 [k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "w"'
@walk turn=w cond='WAY != "w"'
[texton]
Someone has placed a large rock at the entrance of the path, as if they don't want anyone to enter.[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
